-- Formula One Driver Robert Kubica is Injured in Rally Car Crash, Ansa Says
-- B y   S o n i a   S i r l e t t i
-- 2011-02-06T11:00:59Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-06/f1-driver-robert-kubica-injured-in-rally-car-crash-ansa-says.html
Renault Formula 1 driver  Robert Kubica  has been seriously injured in a crash during a rally race
in  Italy , the Ansa news agency reported.  Kubica was driving a Skoda Fabia in the Super2000 category
of the Rally Ronde di Andora when his car overturned, the news
agency said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Sonia Sirletti in Milan at 
